        Python docstring-based documentation generator for lazy perfectionists.
        
        - [üôå Handsdown - Python documentation generator](#%f0%9f%99%8c-handsdown---python-documentation-generator)
          - [üî¨ Features](#%f0%9f%94%ac-features)
